name: Pair_allMatchTest
description: Unit tests for the Pair.allMatch method, which checks if all elements in two iterables match based on a given predicate.

test_cases.name: testAllMatch_True
test_cases.description: Tests the Pair.allMatch method with two iterables where all elements match based on the predicate.

test_cases.name: testAllMatch_False
test_cases.description: Tests the Pair.allMatch method with two iterables where not all elements match based on the predicate.

test_cases.name: testAllMatch_DifferentLengths
test_cases.description: Tests the Pair.allMatch method with two iterables of different lengths.

test_cases.name: testAllMatch_EmptyIterables
test_cases.description: Tests the Pair.allMatch method with two empty iterables.
